item.dc:creator: @kevlord kevlord
item.description:
@kevlord wrote:

  1. in client.java search wanneshop, you will see something like this } else if (NPCID == id) { //shop PutNPCCoords = true; WanneShop = shopid;

  2. click at the last ; and press enter and add this } else if (NPCID == id) { //banker PutNPCCoords = true; openUpBank();

dont forgot to put the npc id.
